{
  "text": "Static transformation from high level languages like C into fine-grained reconfigurable logic is still the research focus of a number of academic and commercial research groups. Only very few of them support the full programming language [CITATION_1] .",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "15690675"
